      "message": "Align designer CLI usage and fix hardcoded /extra-skills paths (#85)\n\nAfter fastclaw PR #56 remapped the ecap-skills mount point, the hardcoded\n/extra-skills/... paths no longer resolve. In addition, the designer skill's\nimage_generation_cli.py renamed --image-urls to --images and changed stdout\nfrom JSON to a plain file path.\n\nChanges:\n- Replace --image-urls with --images across all bash examples and docs\n  (stylist-agent, soulmate-pack)\n- Replace /extra-skills/<skill>/... with ~/.openclaw/skills/<skill>/...\n  so the path resolves via $HOME at runtime\n  (bash blocks use tilde expansion; Python subprocess uses os.path.expanduser)\n- Update generate_collage.py fallback_generate() to parse the new plain\n  stdout format and widen its return type to str | None\n\nAffected agents: stylist-agent, soulmate-pack, restaurant-review-monitor,\nzoodance-vibe-drama.\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
